OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FThe England manager's role has long
OL,7,Fbeen described as the 'impossible job'
OL,8,Fbut recent evidence suggests that
OL,9,Flabel should actually apply to whoever
OL,10,Fis in charge at Manchester United.
OL,12,FRuben Amorim becomes the sixth
OL,13,Fpermanent boss at Old Trafford since
OL,14,FSir Alex Ferguson handed over the
OL,15,Freins to David Moyes in the summer of
OL,16,F2013.
