OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FNone can so far be considered a real
OL,7,Fsuccess, least of all Erik ten Hag,
OL,8,Fwho when he was fired had presided
OL,9,Fover United's worst-ever start to a
OL,10,FPremier League season.
OL,12,FAmorim's appointment is of course the
OL,13,Fmost significant decision made by the
OL,14,FIneos executive team since they took
OL,15,Fcontrol of all things football earlier
OL,16,Fthis year.
OL,18,FA statement released on Friday said
OL,19,FAmorim has signed a contract until
OL,20,FJune 2027 with a club option of an
OL,21,Fadditional year.
