OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FThey considered letting the Dutchman
OL,7,Fgo last summer but decided, after
OL,8,Fbeating neighbours City in the FA Cup
OL,9,Ffinal, to not only keep him but extend
OL,10,Fhis contract, which boosted his
OL,11,Fcompensation package.
OL,13,FSo changing their minds so soon
OL,14,Fafterwards has been costly and is an
OL,15,Funcomfortable look for Sir Jim, who
OL,16,Fhas been cost cutting in every
OL,17,Fdepartment at Old Trafford.
