OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FFrom Sir Alex's ambassadorial deal to
OL,7,Fhundreds of job losses and company
OL,8,Fcredit cards being cancelled, amongst
OL,9,Fmany other measures - no one has been
OL,10,Fsafe from the Ineos guillotine.
OL,12,FAmorim's curtain raiser will be away
OL,13,Fat newly promoted - and winless -
OL,14,FIpswich.
OL,16,FNot only will this be his first match
OL,17,Fin his new role, it will also be his
OL,18,Ffirst match as manager of a club
OL,19,Foutside Portugal.
