OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FHe has a good reputation having led
OL,7,FSporting to their first league title
OL,8,Fin 19 years, and subsequently repeated
OL,9,Fthat feat, along with capturing a
OL,10,Fcouple of Portuguese Cup trophies, all
OL,11,Finside four years.
OL,13,FBut the Primeira Liga is not the
OL,14,FPremier League, despite the fact that
OL,15,FAmorim attracted interest from West
OL,16,FHam United and reportedly Manchester
OL,17,FCity too for post-Guardiola.
OL,19,FThe past weeks have played out like
OL,20,Fsomething of a soap opera, so the
OL,21,FIpswich game can't come soon enough.
