OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FBy January we should be able to assess
OL,7,Fhow shrewd the choice of Amorim has
OL,8,Fbeen, and by extension whether finally
OL,9,Fthe Ineos era will have provided
OL,10,FUnited fans with something to shout
OL,11,Fabout.
OL,13,FManchester United's statement in full
OL,15,FManchester United is delighted to
OL,16,Fannounce the appointment of Ruben
OL,17,FAmorim as Head Coach of the men's
OL,18,Ffirst team, subject to work visa
OL,19,Frequirements.
