OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FHe will join until June 2027 with a
OL,7,Fclub option of an additional year once
OL,8,Fhe has fulfilled his obligations to
OL,9,Fhis current club. He will join
OL,10,FManchester United on Monday 11
OL,11,FNovember.
OL,13,FRuben is one of the most exciting and
OL,14,Fhighly rated young coaches in European
OL,15,Ffootball. Highly decorated as both a
OL,16,Fplayer and coach, his titles include
OL,17,Fwinning the Primeira Liga twice in
OL,18,FPortugal with Sporting CP; the first
OL,19,Fof which was the club's first title in
OL,20,F19 years.
